Site description

This website has been designed with the United States traveller in mind. This could be an individual or a family.
The main page is designed with a quick reference to different places in the United States to visit. There is a contact or email page
as well as an about page. At this stage the site is designed to give details of different locations with the intent to add possible
links to travel sites where someone can book a hotel or rental car in preparation for their trip.
